data.description:
This charming 3-bedroom, 1.1-bath property is a true gem. The first thing you'll notice is the inviting atmosphere as you step inside. A cozy fireplace graces the living area, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance for gatherings.
The heart of this home is the updated kitchen, boasting modern appliances and stylish finishes. It's a chef's delight with plenty of counter space and storage, making meal preparation a breeze.
Three spacious bedrooms offer comfort and versatility, perfect for accommodating a growing family or creating a home office. The convenience of a half-bath adjoining the master bedroom adds a touch of luxury to your daily routine.
This property offers an extra layer of security with its storm shelter, providing peace of mind during severe weather. A new roof is in the works, ensuring that you'll have worry-free living ahead. Additionally, the cost of foundation repairs will be set aside at closing, eliminating any potential concerns.
Location, location, location! This home is ideally situated for those working at Tinker Air Force Base, with quick and easy access to both I-40 and I-240. Commuting to downtown Oklahoma City is a breeze, saving you valuable time and stress.
With all these features, it's a rare find and an incredible opportunity for a lucky buyer. Don't miss your chance to make this home your own. Schedule a showing now and step into the comfort, convenience, and style that awaits you!
